    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“Grief like a stray dog”（《悲伤如狗随行》）是一部简短的互动叙事作品，故事发生在二战时期：一位年轻的邮递员肩负着向士兵家属传达前线消息的任务——那些消息常常是可怖的死讯。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831800/extras/0f4db154fdfe686ad0ca936d526a992c.poster.avif?t=1764607888\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831800/extras/0f4db154fdfe686ad0ca936d526a992c.webm?t=1764607888\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831800/extras/0f4db154fdfe686ad0ca936d526a992c.mp4?t=1764607888\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主人公的创作灵感源于游戏制作人的祖母，以及塔季扬娜·切尔诺夫斯卡娅（Tatyana Chernovskaya）的《关于邮递员的诗》中的女主角。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事根植于在勒热夫附近村落的童年回忆，那里曾是二战中极惨烈、血腥的战场。次要人物的命运、生活片段、境遇几乎都取材于家族口述史、战争回忆、先人的信件以及一些公开资料。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831800/extras/8fd6eb66bfe96b12eac1d6d6f7ad2959.poster.avif?t=1764607888\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831800/extras/8fd6eb66bfe96b12eac1d6d6f7ad2959.webm?t=1764607888\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831800/extras/8fd6eb66bfe96b12eac1d6d6f7ad2959.mp4?t=1764607888\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >艺术风格受启发于儿童绘画、新表现主义、俄罗斯民间艺术卢博克（lubok）以及苏联时期的书籍插图。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >图像、回忆、思考和对关键时刻的描绘构成了《悲伤如狗随行》的美学空间，同时融合了俄罗斯民间故事的常见母题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 你将体验到：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >带有冒险游戏元素的视觉小说。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扎根于回忆和俄罗斯民间传说，丰富深刻的故事。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手绘2D风格。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >令人不安且独特的配乐。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >简洁真实的对话。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏时长：60-80分钟。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >充满鲜活人物的村庄。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831800/extras/6259b50392812fb82e1051d758411510.poster.avif?t=1764607888\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831800/extras/6259b50392812fb82e1051d758411510.webm?t=1764607888\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
